column1: IF ccr_zob_dhf_d is MF 1 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1

IF ccr_ll_oxo_etio_d is MF 2 AND ccr_saad3a17b_d is MF 0 AND ccr_cortisone_d is MF 2 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_pt_one_d is MF 0 AND ccr_the_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
